# Migrations

- **Do not run `makemigrations`** in this project — **write migration files manually** (see `CLAUDE.md`: tooling constraints).
- **Schema** changes and **data** changes belong in **separate** migration files.
- **Seed / reference data**: use **data migrations**, not fixtures; prefer **`get_or_create`** so migrations are safe to re-run.
- Name migrations descriptively, e.g. `0003_add_profile_models`, `0004_seed_roles`.
